<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>CLASS SELECTOR</title>
    <style>
        .abc{
            background-color: blue;
            color: beige;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 class="abc"> CLASS SELECTOR </h1>
    <h1 class="abc"> CLASS SELECTOR </h1>
</body>
</html>
<!--By using class selector we can apply css styles for group of elements.
it is represented by using '.'-->
